<table width="95%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tr>
<td><font class="pn-title"><a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=3&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">The History of the Knights of the Green Mist…</a></font><br>
<font class="pn-normal"><p align="justify" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0"><i><font color="#800000" size="3" face="Times New Roman">&quot;So it is that was born a special group of Iksar bent on the freedom of their race, no longer closed minded about the enemies of their people.  These Knights remember that it was a Devine Act that gave them their freedom and they look back to the time of the Green Mists for inspiration in the days ahead.  So did they form the Knights of the Green Mist, drawing not only from the ranks of all the groups of the Iksar but also enlisting the aid of the softskins of like mind. The Knights operate outside of the boundaries of the rulers of Cabilis. They have one, and only one true goal: the destruction of the greatest threat ever known to all of Norrath, the Dragon menace. To this end have they sought out many of the soft skinned races and found those that too realize the threat the Dragon pose to all races and joined together to exterminate this threat…&quot;<br />
</font></i><p align="right" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0"><i><font color="#800000" size="3" face="Times New Roman"><B>~ Zarkorsis Kunzar</B><br />
On the <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/modules.php?op=modload&name=News&file=article&sid=3&mode=thread&order=0&thold=0">History of the Knights</a></font></i></p></font><br>
<font class="pn-sub">Published Aug 12, 2002 - 07:36 PM</font>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</p>
